WEBVTT

00:00:58.631 --> 00:01:01.391
vyote hivi unavyoshughulika navyo
kila siku

00:01:01.391 --> 00:01:03.751
zinageuka kua michoro ya elektroniki?

00:01:03.751 --> 00:01:05.373
Na kama je vinatoa taarifa nyingi

00:01:05.373 --> 00:01:10.350
kuhusu wewe ni nani kama michoro
inavyofanya?

00:01:10.350 --> 00:01:12.536
Kilichotokea miongo michache iliopita

00:01:12.536 --> 00:01:15.642
ni aina ya kinga anayopata kama mkuu
wa nchi

00:01:15.642 --> 00:01:18.321
au mtu mkubwa mashuhuri

00:01:18.321 --> 00:01:21.042
sasa inatumika kila siku na watu wote hawa

00:01:21.042 --> 00:01:24.029
ambao wana twiti, blogu, wanaokufuata,

00:01:24.029 --> 00:01:28.349
wanaoangalia alama zako za mikopo na
unachojifanyia mwenyewe.

00:01:28.349 --> 00:01:32.763
Na michoro ya elektroniki pia ina kelele.